name: Brazilian Curly
description: The texture of the hair is beautiful and soft. There’s no shedding or tangling, the hair will last over a year or more if it properly care for. It can be flat-ironed, dye or curled, all cuticles in the same direction. Use shampoo and conditioner to wash the hair.  All cuticles should be same direction.  We measure the length of hair when the hair is stretched.
